    "name": "Emergency Exit",
    "steam_appid": 3159620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/a43e335ad01654c7ad740c96c1ba5c78.avif?t=1768313358\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📄 <strong>PROTOCOL EE-3159620 — INFORMATION FILE FOR TEST SUBJECTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sender:</strong> Telescreen Defense Corp — Department of Cooperative Experiments<br><strong>Recipients:</strong> Voluntary subjects assigned to the <i>EMERGENCY EXIT</i> simulation<br><strong>Subject:</strong> General instructions for participation and obligations</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦ <strong>PREAMBLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I, the undersigned, voluntary test subject, acknowledge that the <i>EMERGENCY EXIT</i> program (EE-3159620 – 2025) is a cooperative simulation.<br>This simulation evaluates the subjects’ ability to communicate, solve complex problems, and act under pressure in a hostile environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I understand that my chances of success depend exclusively on my coordination with the partner assigned to me.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▣ <strong>SIMULATION MODALITIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two operators. Two distinct roles. One single exit.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✦ <strong>Operator 1</strong><br>• Alone in the corridors of the complex.<br>• Equipped with a simple flashlight with limited battery.<br>• Progresses through a dark evacuation plan, exposed to flames, traps, and biological anomalies.<br>• Must demonstrate orientation, observation, and composure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/e8ff91f72b2fa3f3c1a09b8b5e63ecc6.poster.avif?t=1768313358\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/e8ff91f72b2fa3f3c1a09b8b5e63ecc6.webm?t=1768313358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/e8ff91f72b2fa3f3c1a09b8b5e63ecc6.mp4?t=1768313358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>▣ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▣ <strong>Operator 2</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Confined to the control room.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Cannot see Operator 1.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Guides their partner using the provided emergency manual.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Controls and monitors the environment to allow progression, while managing the power supply on which the various systems depend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/a6e4f54bd77de8a8bc50a2c02749edc8.poster.avif?t=1768313358\" width=616 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/a6e4f54bd77de8a8bc50a2c02749edc8.webm?t=1768313358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/a6e4f54bd77de8a8bc50a2c02749edc8.mp4?t=1768313358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◈ <strong>OBJECTIVES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☐ Reach the exit before the time runs out.<br>☐ Maintain clear and continuous communication.<br>☐ Solve the puzzles and challenges encountered together.<br>☐ Discover the journals and documents left by previous test subjects.<br>☐ Achieve the best scores and surpass other subjects.<br>☐ Complete the experience in both roles to finalize your file and validate your contract.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/029a8fcfb7d6a9820724575b35bd5f09.poster.avif?t=1768313358\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/029a8fcfb7d6a9820724575b35bd5f09.webm?t=1768313358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/029a8fcfb7d6a9820724575b35bd5f09.mp4?t=1768313358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▣ <strong>ADDITIONAL NOTES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Several difficulty levels are available (and additional game modes to come).<br>• Two final outcomes are recorded.<br>• The simulation contains optional and secret elements to discover.<br>• The results will be archived in your personal file.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/c2f5315ead3ecc8a855a6939116bfaf0.poster.avif?t=1768313358\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/c2f5315ead3ecc8a855a6939116bfaf0.webm?t=1768313358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/c2f5315ead3ecc8a855a6939116bfaf0.mp4?t=1768313358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✦ <strong>REMARKS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Emergency Exit does not offer a traditional tutorial. This is a deliberate choice.</i><br><br><br><br><br><i>The game invites you to discover its mechanics and rules through exploration and experimentation, and rewards curiosity and observation.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/b27788b787a7119085388b695f831309.poster.avif?t=1768313358\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/b27788b787a7119085388b695f831309.webm?t=1768313358\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/b27788b787a7119085388b695f831309.mp4?t=1768313358\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please also confirm your participation by adding this program to your wishlist.<br>Thank you for your cooperation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras/4085d33945ef66417848463457c6cefb.webp?t=1768313358\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159620/extras_big/4085d33945ef66417848463457c6cefb.webp?t=1768313358 width=800 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
